    "Each category is discussed in detail, providing relevant introductions and explanations.",
    "To enhance readers' understanding, the survey also introduces common public datasets and evaluation methods used in the field of 3D-PCPR.",
    "Additionally, it compares the performance of mainstream methods in 3D-PCPR to highlight the algorithm performance of various methods.",
